"     * Different progestins are not equivalent on a milligram basis.",
"     <br/>",
"     <span class=\"bullet\">",
"      &bull;",
"     </span>",
"     Ethinyl estradiol and mestranol are not equivalent on a milligram basis; the results of some studies indicate that 30-35 mcg of ethinyl estradiol is equivalent to 50 mcg of mestranol.",
